entries.femaleVariant: Ah, you are here.
What're we doin' here?
Do you know who most wished to honor Arasaka-sama with the parade?
Don't see what that gets us.
Thought Yori wasn't one for tradition.
What's in it for Yorinobu?
Parade stands to confirm his legitimacy.
Yorinobu's a smart little muffin. Puttin' on the parade to show off his attachment to Arasaka, its values.
He is shrewd. I will not deny that.
Japanese heritage is one element. Yorinobu will also put on a display of power.
The floats are sure to be beautiful, but the wizened eye will see in them a hidden message to his foes.
Still don't see how this gets us anywhere.
I acquired some information of my own.
I have had an idea.
Look to the sky.
While you were occupied with your shady dealings, I learned more about the floats.
I have an infected shard.
[Take shard]
And then?
Hacking's not my forte.
Right. Then what?
Gotta be honest. Netrunning's not my forte.
It is even less mine.
They are all kept in one place – Arasaka Industrial Park. It is there that they prepare them.
Let us move on.
To take control of the float is one thing, but not all. The security concerns me – the snipers especially. I will be an easy target.
But I may have an answer. Okada-san mentioned the city cameras.
Doesn't seem like the kind who'd care to honor tradition.
That is so.
<mothertongue l="jpn" m="gumin-domo" b="\"I am here, " a=". Watch your backs.\" "/>
What message'd that be?
And to solidify his legitimacy.
Good to see you, Goro.
Goro. Good to see you.
Why? What're we doin' here?
As it is to see you, V.
Actually sounds doable.
Lots of ways to skin this particular cat, y'know. Gonna need--
I know what you need. It is taken care of.
It was not cheap, but the man who sold it to me guaranteed it will work.
And how ya aim to do that?
In front of everyone? Think you might've lost it.
Impossible. Even with implants.
And how ya aim to manage that?
You're gnatshit crazy. In front of a crowd? What about security or...?
Expectation's way too high, Goro. Couldn't pull that off even if you had your fancy implants.
entries.maleVariant: Expectation's way too high, Goro. Couldn't pull that off even if you still had your fancy implants.

entries.femaleVariant: We need only to break into the compound, find the right float and inject a virus into its system.
You will then be able to disable any security before I sneak inside.
I have thought of a solution.
You need not worry.
Think I see where this is goin'. Got me doin' all the dirty work.
Do you wish to trade places? What exactly would you say to her? "Hello, my name is V"?
Hanako-sama knows me. Only I can do this.
Not one for subtlety, is he?
I do not understand. Does Arasaka not have enough of its own people?
Look around, sir. Things're heating up in the city.
Not one to butt in, but…
Need to steal your buddy for a second.
Hate to interrupt, but...
He's got the gift of the gab, can't be denied, but I need to steal your buddy for a sec.
Ah, perfect timing!
What are you...?
The dashi floats will pass precisely this way.
If I could just get onto Hanako-sama's float, I could speak with her in private.
Get there how?
Shard – where'd you get it?
Where'd you get this shard?
Across the canal.
Kabuki? Might actually be half-decent soft, then.
And if it isn't, got a few tricks up my sleeve, too.
An' riots're always best put down by folks not sportin' your brand name.
Suits know one spark's all it takes for Japantown to go up in flames.
Why, jump, of course.
You shall learn soon.
Sounds like a plan.
Why's the dirty work my job?
Sounds like a plan.
You agree just like that? The risks are considerable.
Yeah, well – gettin' more 'n' more used to that.
His murderer. The irony makes me sick.
This is good to know.
And now... what would you say to a small test? We must try the shard.
The camera control room is in front of us.
You must get inside and infect the network, that is all.
Uh-huh. And in the meantime you'll do what? Crack open a can o' suds?
I would not touch alcohol at work. I will watch your back. Now, get to it.
If we gain access to them, we will see exactly where the snipers are. You can deal with them as I advance.
[Wait]
[Stand]
